{"tid":902899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【胞姊按掣火化】儀式僅五分鐘 親友灑淚送別藍潔瑛","createTime":"2018-11-15T06:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T06:49:44.000Z","uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"785ab31ced494b7802c83cbc0b59e85d76c9c7e3","tid":902899,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"【胞姊按掣火化】儀式僅五分鐘 親友灑淚送別藍潔瑛<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181115&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58914917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181115%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58914917&d=ZWcZKNvS28CkH%2Fe%2BhxUukJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=bd13b835\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181115%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58914917&h=a3c8cb9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181115&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58914917</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMzOAcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMzOAcn.png&h=7d84bbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本月初離世的藍潔瑛，遺體今日進行火化，早上近10時，胞姐藍潔卿在親友陪同下，到域多利亞殮房領回藍潔瑛的遺體後，眾人乘靈車抵達歌連臣角火葬場。<br />\n<br />\n早上約11時許，靈車抵達了火葬場進行儀式，親友陪她走最後一程，藍潔瑛的白色靈柩上刻有十字架，寫上「藍潔瑛魂歸天國」，棺上放有一束鮮花，由陳志明副主教主持天主教儀式。<br />\n儀式大約5分鐘，陳副主教撒聖水，讀經文後，領眾親屬向藍潔瑛遺體鞠躬，胞姐除下黑帽致意，女親屬難忍悲痛落淚，胞姐亦表現傷感，最後由胞姐負責最後撳掣儀式，藍潔瑛的棺木進行火化，回歸天國主懷安息。<br />\n<br />\n儀式完結後，男親友捧着藍潔瑛遺照放入焚化爐火化，之後藍胞姐步離火葬場，問到藍潔瑛骨灰安放在何處？女親友說：「長沙灣」，相信是長沙灣天主教墳場，之後眾人再乘坐靈車離"},{"pid":"7aac2168f9ed444f30a55802569d7e298be1a992","tid":902899,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATHAfcL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATHAfcL.png&h=db2aee73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcjShq6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcjShq6.png&h=51cbe577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"